RC.DescriptionEn:
If additional declaration type is X or Y, MRN is required,
else if additional declaration type is Z, MRN is optional (depending if exists I2 notification),
else not used.

If dataset type is H1, then this is required,
else if dataset type is H3, H4 or H5E, then this is optional,
else not used.

IF Dataset type = H2 then this is required, 
else if dataset type is H5P then this is not used,
else optional

If dataset type is H5N or H5P, then this is not used,
else if dataset type is I1 and requested procedure is different than 42 or 63, then this is optional,
else this is required.

If dataset type is H5N, H5P or H2, then this is not used,
else if dataset type is H5E and declaration is lodged by private person, then this is optional,
else it is not used.

If dataset type is H5N or H7, then CN code is not used,
else if dataset type is H2, then CN code is optional,
else if dataset type is H1 or H5E, CN code is required (unless NC0223 applies).

If dataset type is H5N or H7, then Taric code is not used,
else if dataset type is H2 or H5E, then Taric code is optional,
else if dataset type is H1, Taric code is required (unless NC0223 applies).

If dataset type is H5P, H5N or H2, then this is not used,
else if dataset type is I1, then this is optional,
else this is required (or as other conditions suggest)..

If additional declaration type is  U, then this is required,
else if additional declaration type is V, then this is conditional (NR1014),
else this is not used.

If dataset type is H5N or H5P, then this is not used,
else if dataset type is H2 or (H5E lodged by private person), then this is optional,
else this is required.

If dataset type is H2 or H5P,
then this is not used,
else required (or as other conditions apply)

If additional declaration type is U, V then additional information code FIPER with description "W" or "M"  is required ,
else if additional declaration type is C, F or case is presentation notification I2 then additional information code FIPER with description "W" or "M"  is optional,
else additional information FIPER cannot be used.
